article_title: Buzz Davis: Are superdelegates the Godfathers of the Democratic 1 percenters?
article_text:
Madison, WI (53711)

Today

Cloudy this morning. Scattered thunderstorms developing this afternoon. High 77F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 60%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening. Cloudy skies after midnight. Low 64F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

og.description: Grass-roots progressives are fighting back against the power of the superdelegates in order to award superdelegates to Sanders and Clinton in proportion to the votes they received in the primary.
